<paragraph blockId="25.[189,653,1871,1903]" box="[189,653,1871,1903]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">
<heading box="[189,653,1871,1903]" centered="true" fontSize="12" level="2" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" reason="2">
3.4 Genus 
<taxonomicName authority="CAMERON, 1939" authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[320,653,1871,1903]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[320,451,1871,1903]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Zyrastilbus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="CAMERON, M." box="[459,653,1871,1903]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" refId="ref33457" refString="CAMERON, M. 1939: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae. Volume IV Parts I-II. - SEWELL, R. B. S. (ed): The Fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. - London: 691 pp." type="book" year="1939">CAMERON, 1939</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="88" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="25.[151,756,1929,2082]" lastBlockId="25.[794,1399,233,802]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,262,1929,1953]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Comment</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[287,402,1929,1953]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[287,402,1929,1953]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Zyrastilbus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation author="CAMERON, M." pageId="25" pageNumber="88" refId="ref33457" refString="CAMERON, M. 1939: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae. Volume IV Parts I-II. - SEWELL, R. B. S. (ed): The Fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. - London: 691 pp." type="book" year="1939">CAMERON (1939)</bibRefCitation>
to include only 
<taxonomicName authority="CAMERON, 1939" authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[399,756,1961,1985]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyras" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="almorensis">
<emphasis box="[399,575,1961,1985]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Zyras almorensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="CAMERON, M." box="[583,756,1961,1985]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" refId="ref33457" refString="CAMERON, M. 1939: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae. Volume IV Parts I-II. - SEWELL, R. B. S. (ed): The Fauna of British India, including Ceylon and Burma. - London: 691 pp." type="book" year="1939">CAMERON, 1939</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from North 
<collectingCountry box="[280,338,1993,2017]" name="India" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">India</collectingCountry>
, the 
<typeStatus box="[387,433,1994,2018]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">type</typeStatus>
species by monotypy. According to 
<bibRefCitation author="HLAVAC, P. &amp; NEWTON, A. F. &amp; MARUYAMA, M." box="[222,446,2025,2053]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="1 - 151" refId="ref33502" refString="HLAVAC, P.; NEWTON, A. F. &amp; MARUYAMA, M. 2011: World catalogue of the species of the tribe Lomechusini (Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Zootaxa 3075: 1 - 151." type="journal article" year="2011">HLAVÁČ et al. (2011)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[457,572,2025,2049]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[457,572,2025,2049]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Zyrastilbus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been treated as a distinct genus since 
<bibRefCitation author="PACE, R." box="[412,544,2057,2081]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="243 - 302" refId="ref34278" refString="PACE, R. 2004: Aleocharinae di Thailandia, Cambogia, Laos e Malaysia (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Belgian Journal of Entomology 6: 243 - 302." type="journal article" year="2004">PACE (2004)</bibRefCitation>
, and two additional species have subsequently been assigned to this taxon: 
<taxonomicName authority="(PACE, 1998)" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[794,1019,265,289]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adesi">
<emphasis box="[794,875,265,289]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. adesi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="PACE, R." box="[892,1012,265,289]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="911 - 982" refId="ref34103" refString="PACE, R. 1998: Aleocharinae della Cina: Parte IV (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 105 (4): 911 - 982." type="journal article" year="1998">PACE, 1998</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="PACE, 2004" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1075,1355,265,289]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[1075,1224,265,289]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. angkorensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="PACE, R." box="[1233,1355,265,289]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="243 - 302" refId="ref34278" refString="PACE, R. 2004: Aleocharinae di Thailandia, Cambogia, Laos e Malaysia (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Belgian Journal of Entomology 6: 243 - 302." type="journal article" year="2004">PACE, 2004</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. An examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[1017,1063,298,322]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">type</typeStatus>
material of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[1207,1346,297,321]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyras" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="almorensis">
<emphasis box="[1207,1346,297,321]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. almorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[794,875,329,353]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adesi">
<emphasis box="[794,875,329,353]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. adesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as well as the details and illustrations provided in the original description of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1146,1295,361,385]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[1146,1295,361,385]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. angkorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
revealed that neither 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[935,1016,393,417]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adesi">
<emphasis box="[935,1016,393,417]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. adesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
nor 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1077,1226,393,417]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[1077,1226,393,417]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. angkorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are congeneric with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[850,989,425,449]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyras" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="almorensis">
<emphasis box="[850,989,425,449]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. almorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; for arguments regarding the generic assignment of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1998" box="[962,1043,457,481]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adesi">
<emphasis box="[962,1043,457,481]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. adesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
see the section on 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="PACE" baseAuthorityYear="1998" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Pheidologitonetes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adesi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Pheidologitonetes adesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. As can be inferred from the description and the illustrations in 
<bibRefCitation author="PACE, R." box="[1065,1203,521,545]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="243 - 302" refId="ref34278" refString="PACE, R. 2004: Aleocharinae di Thailandia, Cambogia, Laos e Malaysia (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Belgian Journal of Entomology 6: 243 - 302." type="journal article" year="2004">PACE (2004)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1220,1369,521,545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[1220,1369,521,545]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. angkorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="CAMERON" authorityYear="1939" box="[1009,1148,553,577]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyras" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="almorensis">
<emphasis box="[1009,1148,553,577]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. almorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by significant external and sexual characters, especially the completely different habitus (including the shapes of the head and the pronotum), a completely different antennal morphology, and a relatively large and voluminous spermatheca. The true generic assignment (
<taxonomicName authorityName="LEACH" authorityYear="1819" box="[1076,1161,713,737]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Drusilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1076,1161,713,737]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Drusilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
?) of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2004" box="[1222,1371,713,737]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Zyrastilbus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angkorensis">
<emphasis box="[1222,1371,713,737]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">Z. angkorensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is currently unknown and can be clarified only based on an examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[1000,1046,778,802]" pageId="25" pageNumber="88">type</typeStatus>
material.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
